name: CakeWalk
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cake walk
des: The app prompts the user to mention their day, month and year of birth. If any of these three are omitted, Alexa will prompt them a second time. After learning the day, month, and year, Alexa stores them in AWS for next time. Upon starting Cake Walk after your birthday is already stored, it will calculate and state how many days until your next birthday.
